remarks.format: ## Remarks 通过访问的属性名称和值 将保持最新状态，并且可在项目的整个生成中进行枚举。The property names and values accessed through are kept up-to-date and can be enumerated throughout the build of the project. 但是，更改此列表中的属性不会影响生成过程。However, changing a property in this list will not affect the build process. > [!NOTE] > 此属性不适用于多处理器生成。This property does not work with multi-proc builds. 若要获得正确的结果，可以通过指定默认) (来关闭多处理器生成 `/m:1` ，也可以通过设置环境变量来解决此限制。To get proper results, you can either turn off multi-proc building by specifying `/m:1` (which is the default), or you can work around the limitation by setting an environment variable. 例如，设置 `MSBuildForwardPropertiesFromChild=configuration;platform` 从子节点转发 "配置" 和 "平台" 属性。For example, setting `MSBuildForwardPropertiesFromChild=configuration;platform` forwards the "configuration" and "platform" properties from the child nodes. 除非定义了此环境变量，否则将不会转发任何内容。Unless this environment variable is defined, nothing will be forwarded. 有关详细信息，请参阅 [如何：在生成中使用环境变量](/visualstudio/msbuild/how-to-use-environment-variables-in-a-build)。For more information, see [How to: Use Environment Variables in a Build](/visualstudio/msbuild/how-to-use-environment-variables-in-a-build).
